></div><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26=
px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>I don&#8217;t think AI will replace humans. =
My bet is that we&#8217;ll end up in a </span><a href=3D"https://substack.c=
om/redirect/2b62a48e-df1d-4476-8202-88cbed40cf42?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8=
